  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>It counts as a whip for jutsu requirements. Additionally, you may choose to add either Silky Cream or Shampoo to your hair, not being able to change this choice once picked.</p><ul><li><p>Silky Cream: Your hair is much smoother than before, allowing you to attack enemies at a faster pace. When making an attack with your hair-whip, you may make two attacks instead of one.</p></li><li><p>Shampoo: Your hair has been strengthened from the power of Shampoo, causing those who are hit by it to feel even more pain. Your hairwhip gains the Critical keyword and adds your proficiency bonus to its damage.</p></li></ul>",
